27:
What's wrong? You thought this was
enough...
35:
What will it be, Alk? The dragon stirs!
In but a moment, your beloved
reality will be wiped away!
38:
What is it you plan to do, Alk? Tell
me!
56:
I won't let the likes of a dragon get in
my way!
61:
Stand tall, warriors! Keep fighting,
and prove your mettle!
65:
The ground forces are already back
up! They've still got fight left in them!
69:
Suizen and the others seem okay as
well. Things are still—
73:
The anti-air section has been hit!
Damage sustained—
77:
Apologies, mon capitaine! Seems
we took a hit. The crew are
uninjured, but I would still
recommend evacuation. What are
your orders?
80:
Agreed. Proceed with the
evacuation!
Are YOU okay, Regis?
83:
Oh, half my body appears to have
been blown off—it's probably rolling
around here somewhere. Nothing a
little wrench work can't fix!
90:
I'm the ship's beakhead, right? Let
me slam into that dragon, like I did
before!
94:
A ramming maneuver? It could
work... What do you think, Captain?
104:
C'mon, why not?! It worked against
that Devourer of Stars thing, didn't it?
109:
Don't be silly. The way things are
now—
116:
Why have you come here? What is it
you seek to accomplish?
124:
And we have no intention of giving
ANY of them up.
127:
And what about you? Sneaking
aboard a ship like some
stowaway—what's your deal?
132:
This one wishes to save "her." Both of
her.
137:
Cap'n, look! Stella and Leve are
completely surrounded... And
Nimbus isn't looking too good either!
142:
*pant* It'll be a cold day in hell...
before I let even a single one... of you
bastards through!
157:
It is because of "her" that this one
has gained a soul. Newcomers...
Lend me your aid.
162:
Amelia! Nao and I are deploying to
the surface. Can you helm the ship?!
167: Aye-aye, Czarina! Leave it to me!
176: I'm here! Hop on my back, Marina!
180:
Hey! Don't hog all the fun! I call dibs
on carrying Nao!
185: We're all set... Here we go!
189:
Ready the main and auxiliary
dracocannons! Annie! Sully!
Rammy! Va-va! You all good?
193:
Va-va?! Mind your impertinent
tongue, you—
199:
Time for a laser show to get some
attention off of my beloved Czarina!
Fire away!
207:
Dragons, you attack from above! I'll
cover Nimbus!
214:
Make sure to give that brother of
yours an earful while you're at it!
246:
The Antipode Lance! With this, we
could—
250:
What is it you plan to do, Alk? Tell
me!
264: I've had enough of all this!
267: Nova... You're still in there, aren't you?
277:
You remember who I am. You called
me Alk! And...
286: That was Sho's power just now!
290:
Don't you see? You're still you, Nova!
Why can't you understand that...
294:
Why are you trying to make me kill
you?!
302:
Why did you decide to ask me that
now, of all times?
